(<a href="undercoverlearning">Previous review.</a>) 
(Disclosure: I&#8217;ve <a href="visitingla">hung out</a> with 
the author.)</dd>

<dt>Laura Kipnis, <em><a href="http://books.theinfo.org/go/0375719326">Against Love: A Polemic</a></em></dt>
<dd>Kipnis is a rollickingly vicious writer, with sentences that have the 
