(<a href="againstlove">Previous review.</a>)</dd>

<dt>Matt Taibbi and Mark Ames, <em><a href="http://books.theinfo.org/go/0802136524">The eXile: Sex, Drugs, and Libel in the New Russia</a></em></dt>
<dd>Matt Taibbi is my favorite political journalist. He writes with a raw honesty 
